  cygport-0.9.5
  binutils-20080624-2
  gcc-core-3.4.4-3
  gcc-g++-3.4.4-3
  bash-3.2.39-20
  make-3.81-2
  nasm-2.02-1
  autoconf2.5
  automake1.10
  libtool

Canonical homepage:
  http://tukaani.org/lzma/

Canonical download:
  http://tukaani.org/lzma/download

