==============================================================

Build instructions:
  unpack liblzmadec0-VER-REL-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be unpacked
    under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport liblzmadec0-VER-REL.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/liblzmadec0-VER-REL.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/liblzmadec0-VER-REL-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/liblzmadec-devel-VER-REL.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/leftovers-VER-REL.tar.bz2

